cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.HC. 

The paper deals with the problem of facilitating the search in app stores, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as the authors mention the use of crawling software and the construction of a Knowledge Schema. The development of a Knowledge Graph also involves deep learning (cs.DL) and database systems (cs.DB). Finally, the goal of facilitating user search suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
